  "name": "RPlog_The_Escape_from_Ord_Trasi",
  "title": "The Escape from Ord Trasi",
  "summary": "Fleeing the empty tomb of Davin Keldan, Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin and his dwindling Imperial team, including the pilot Dareus and the Mandalorian Master Sergeant Cantrell, are pursued through the crypts of Ord Trasi by a ravenous swarm of Terentak Sithspawn. As stormtroopers are torn apart, Cantrell buys time with a thermal detonator and Darth Malign emerges from the shadows, carving through the creatures and holding the staircase so the survivors can reach their ship, the Whipping Star. In the Valley of the Damned a final ambush knocks Danik down and his prized Sith Holocron tumbles into an abyss, leaving him with nothing but dead men and despair. Aboard the ship, the wounded Dareus is patched up and the survivors share Corellian whiskey, while Danik, broken by his loss, pledges total loyalty to Malign and asks to become his Sith apprentice. Malign accepts, promising to bring him before his Master Vadim, and demands Danik deliver Johanna's son Etiel into his hands.",
